H0.text: In ‘Othello’, what is the name of Iago’s wife. Bianca

H3.text: In ‘Othello’, what is the name of Iago’s wife. Emilia

A4.text: Iago's wife, Emilia, as Desdemona's attendant.

A5.text: When Othello mentions the handkerchief as proof, Emilia realizes what Iago has done, and she exposes him.

A6.text: Emilia is married to Othello's ensign Iago
